      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready to hit the road? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who values reliability and practical performance! While it shows some honest signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for your commuting needs. It\u2019s a great, budget-friendly option for anyone looking for a trustworthy ride with plenty of miles still to go!",
