      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior shows its age with significant rust on the body panels, several large dents, and clear coat failure across the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is currently slipping. The interior is heavily worn, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest considerable time and resources to get this car back on the road.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
