    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary model maintained to a high standard of mechanical and aesthetic integrity. This automobile offers a refined driving experience, having undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure its performance meets our rigorous criteria for excellence. Characterized by its reliable history and well-preserved interior, it represents a superior acquisition for the discerning motorist who values both sophistication and proven value. Available for immediate delivery to its next steward.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been super well-loved and still runs like a dream. It\u2019s in great shape and ready for its next adventure\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that's been well-maintained. I've kept up with all the service, so it's all set for you to hop in and go. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings have been replaced and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul has been performed. The chassis integrity is reinforced with subframe plates to address common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in and communicative steering rack characteristic of the chassis. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust and the power delivery is linear through the 8,000 RPM redline. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior finish retains a deep shine, showing only the minor road-wear and small stone chips one would expect from a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the upholstery is free of tears, and the dashboard electronics, including the navigation and premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, featuring a documented service history that highlights regular oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With plenty of tread left on the tires and fresh brake pads, this car is ready for the road today without the need for immediate investment.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
